    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total dream! This car is in stunning, flawless condition\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just left the dealership. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always kept in the garage, and you won\u2019t find a single blemish on it. If you want a ride that feels brand new and turns heads everywhere it goes, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
