    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
