    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S54 platform. This specimen features the legendary 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, paired to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the VANOS unit has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings were proactively replaced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with an untouched suspension geometry and a perfectly calibrated Variable M Differential Lock. Finished in pristine Carbon Black, the paint depth is uniform across all panels, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
